OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 11 APR
OL,4,CMISCELLANEOUS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1994FThe BBC Networking Club is
OL,7,Flaunched. BBC: "The BBC's first
OL,8,Fco-ordinated effort on the internet
OL,9,Fbegan with the launch of the BBC
OL,10,FNetworking Club and the supporting
OL,11,Ftelevision programme The Net. The aim
OL,12,Fwas to demystify the information
OL,13,Fsuperhighway - still a novelty for most
OL,14,Fof the population - and offer access to
OL,15,Fthe internet. In the first instance
OL,16,Fthis meant the opening of the BBC
OL,17,Fbulletin board Auntie, to encourage
OL,18,Ffeedback about BBC programmes."
